features: Quilted Northern Ultra Plush toilet paper is designed for optimal softness and premium performance, while cutting down on what you don’t want – lint.
Luxuriously soft toilet paper that's 3X thicker and 3X more absorbent than the leading value toilet tissue brand.
Pamper yourself with 3 cushiony-soft layers in every roll – the perfect combination of soft, silky, and smooth.
Each Mega Roll has 255 3-ply toilet paper sheets and is equal to 4 Quilted Northern Regular Rolls, so you can change the toilet paper rolls less often.
Each toilet paper pack contains 6 Mega Rolls of Quilted Northern Ultra Plush bathroom tissue.
body.description: Treat yourself to the ultimate softness of Quilted Northern Ultra Plush® toilet paper. Featuring 3 cushiony-soft layers in every sheet, Quilted Northern Ultra Plush® bath tissue is 3X thicker and 3X more absorbent than the leading value brand, and you can enjoy all the signature softness without worrying about lint. Quilted Northern Ultra Plush® toilet paper is made from responsibly sourced trees. Each Mega Roll toilet paper has 255 sheets, so in total, you are getting over 1,500 sheets of Quilted Northern Ultra Plush® bathroom tissue! Each toilet tissue pack contains 6 Mega Rolls, equal to 24 Quilted Northern® Regular Rolls, so you can change the roll less often. Pamper yourself with Quilted Northern Ultra Plush® toilet paper for ultimate softness and premium performance.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Quilted Northern Ultra Plush is known for its distinctive feel. Three luxe layers deliver the ultimate in bath tissue softness while cutting down on what you don’t want – lint. There’s no mistaking the luxurious feel of Quilted Northern Ultra Plush toilet paper, thanks to sheets that are 3x thicker and 3x more absorbent than the leading value brand. Our trees come from from well-managed, certified forests and other responsible sources. After all, doing our part to protect our resources matters – to you and us.
